# ADMIN WINDOW REQUIREMENTS

Clicking:

`Manage Artwork`

must:

* open FULL-SCREEN admin management overlay
* overlay entire application
* include circular close button with “X”
* support keyboard ESC close

Admin UI must include:

* Add New Artwork
* Edit Artwork
* Remove Artwork
* Save Artwork
* Logout

