# FAILURE PREVENTION RULES

DO NOT:

* use placeholder code
* omit required features
* generate partial implementations
* break GitHub Pages compatibility
* require build tools
* require backend APIs
* require SQLite runtime
* create fake server routes
* create blinking screens
* create recursive rendering
